snippet.title: South of Midnight - Official Reveal Trailer | Xbox Games Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
The world premiere of South of Midnight showcases story elements for the upcoming game with a skeletal guitar-playing character. South of Midnight will be available on Xbox Game Pass when it's released on Xbox Series X.

#IGN #Xbox #SoG
